Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:25.65,Episode-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(502,297)}Episode 6\N"Punch"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:50.10,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:02:59.90,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.02,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,How about some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.62,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You should take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:13.78,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:14.96,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.19,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:17.55,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.10,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.59,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.29,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.90,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still a little sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.46,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There was a line in a movie:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.19,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,"If a girl of age is sleeping on her stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:56.20,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,it's because she's in love."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:01.99,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I think a parent \Ncan tell regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.08,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any romance movies \Ncalled "You Know What Happens Next",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.47,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:11.98,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You know what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:16.40,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't. But what if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.12,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.31,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.30,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but if you did, you could enjoy it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.87,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.20,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you knew about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.26,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,a future that's a bit sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:34.55,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,at least you can prepare for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.17,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So many perks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:41.64,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,"Enjoy it twice," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.12,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That might be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.61,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I could enjoy the feeling of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.18,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,making a good piece twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.60,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,And in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.30,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,In love—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.15,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.03,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. It was a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.37,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.31,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,A bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.03,Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bug, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:18.78,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good girl, being that she's our girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.66,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but she's of age, so, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:22.42,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Of age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.94,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.18,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's Okikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.24,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Can you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.08,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:39.59,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I never got a chance to hear what you \Nwanted to talk about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:42.51,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I, um, I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.08,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:53.50,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:55.28,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,She just hung up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.56,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That girl from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.73,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:00.35,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Did you mess up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.88,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't experience my first kiss twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.42,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.84,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.46,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,My heart will burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.97,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura-kun, sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.65,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.39,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.80,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.54,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,about the get-together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.13,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:29.91,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.92,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.10,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.88,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I can't be like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.64,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to present myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:54.50,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, sleepy-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.35,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't hear Mom calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.10,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.79,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Breakfast's going to get cold. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.39,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.65,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.65,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I have to swing by somewhere \Nbefore we go to Kazemichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.19,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.34,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I actually
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:28.84,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,had you come early, Touko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.09,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:31.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.41,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,About before—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:35.14,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you were at Sacchan's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:41.62,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she wanted me to know about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:45.36,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But she couldn't say it straight out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.75,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:52.07,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But don't tell Yukinari \Nand Yanagi-san about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.22,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What? Everyone already kno—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.61,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:07:59.86,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.34,Main,Obasan A,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.38,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I did it. I confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.35,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Yana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:25.16,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I like how you're missing\Njust a little bit of tact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:29.44,Main,Obasan A,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.05,Main,Obasan B,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.30,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.62,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get straight to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.71,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:45.30,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's about Sacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.71,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:52.25,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when she couldn't go \Nto the fireworks with us last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:56.19,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought, maybe we could set up \Nfireworks so that she could come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.70,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I do. I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.22,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:03.10,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,We have exams coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.53,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're having too many outings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:06.82,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.42,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let Sacchan know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.16,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.30,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:19.18,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She could talk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.00,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.10,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.39,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,David, probably?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.15,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we can get a hold of him. \NWhy don't we invite him, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.91,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, get Touko to invite him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:32.05,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.11,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:33.63,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.01,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know where he lives, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.99,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.66,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-san, we were saying
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:44.22,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,maybe we should invite David-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.06,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.06,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It just kind of happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:02.85,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.18,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Imi, Okikura-kun's—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:05.79,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.13,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you found my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.75,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okikura is a famous name around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:19.04,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.76,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time, I want to talk outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:50.00,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a complete idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.92,Italics,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Okikura here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.55,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.43,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is Oki... Kakeru-kun—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.62,Italics,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru just went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:06.68,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.64,Italics,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Is Imi-kun a friend of yours, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.29,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.57,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really want to invite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.81,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Then you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:21.99,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:26.21,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just do the things that you want \Nto do. That's not how the world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:27.96,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.16,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,So, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.67,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the fireworks, \Nthe usual group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.31,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm inviting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:34.64,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I see,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.76,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,so you didn't want to invite me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:39.64,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.35,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.40,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.10,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,No reason to cause a stir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:48.35,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You caused a huge stir \Nthe moment you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:49.81,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.68,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing it on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.25,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:54.77,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you enjoying it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:58.77,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. It's circumstantial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:01.24,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you, I'm not doing \Nit because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.36,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.41,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's your relationship with Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.16,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you realized how Touko feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.41,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard anything from Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.96,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,And I have no reason to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.82,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:22.22,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:25.76,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Did Takayama confess to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.72,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to tell me you \Nhaven't answered her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.85,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should skip \Ninviting Kakeru-kun this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.09,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.46,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say it hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:12.64,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:14.44,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.77,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No! No way. Was it Yuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:17.88,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.05,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:20.77,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,No, I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:25.82,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Takayama told him how she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:29.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm being awful to Yuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:32.82,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.42,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, there are a lot of things \NI don't understand lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:39.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,We all chipped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.11,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:42.05,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I bought a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.57,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,We set up the festival for you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.02,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,was supposed to be a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:57.27,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you're being thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.11,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome ba—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:09.82,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.04,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,He's not coming to the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.38,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.29,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:31.09,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Two guys going after Touko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.97,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:34.64,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.96,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.77,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know we can't just leave things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.52,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:59.05,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.04,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,My father's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:02.91,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.71,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,These are all my CDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.27,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. I'm a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:14.20,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:15.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.92,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:25.82,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.20,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Have I found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.21,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom is that pianist—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:16.21,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel calmer when I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:25.96,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.12,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What's your mother like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:30.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's someone who \Ndoesn't stay in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:36.52,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's because of her \Nwork or because of her personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:38.36,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,She must be an active person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.00,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,When I was young,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:43.02,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,it always looked like she was doing\N the right thing no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.98,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that makes me a mama's boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.48,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I feel that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:51.33,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I called you twice already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:55.61,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell me what you \Nwere calling me about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:59.27,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we couldn't talk either time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.32,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan's being hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.92,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,She says it'll be fine, \Nbecause it's just for tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:08.38,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But I've seen her future, in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.43,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.29,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:14.93,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.51,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Yuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.32,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Touko,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.35,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,sorry, there's something I \Nneed to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.52,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,About you punching Okikura-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:25.83,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You met up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.63,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.87,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the school yard. \NLet's settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.67,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You're on my side, right, Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.51,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan, stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:43.33,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get really bad if they meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:54.34,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for punching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:55.59,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:03.97,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:07.44,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,If you really think so,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.23,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,let's have a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:14.41,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We have a perfect field here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.00,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.77,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You? Against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:24.33,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Running is about the only thing you \Ncan take seriously, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:29.40,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, I'll never see Touko again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.87,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, Touko is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.88,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You have Takayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you lose on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.32,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even intend to run, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:54.39,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're after,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:57.28,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,but you're the worst for \Nwhat you chose to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.09,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.45,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.88,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks festival postponed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:33.33,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe David-kun couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,How about just a mini-fireworks festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.78,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true what Yana-chan said?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.47,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I never intended to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.07,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.81,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:56.68,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What was I thinking, starting a fist fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:58.30,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.49,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.93,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't explain anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:04.55,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:08.40,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I just wanted you to say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.93,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,that you're on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.95,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What are the future fragments to you, Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:20.40,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Preparation so I can enjoy things twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.28,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:30.44,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I called them "fragments" \Nof the future because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:34.21,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,they seemed like pieces \Nof me that were missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.56,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Pieces that I need
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:39.35,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,to make my fractured self solid and whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.88,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,But those pieces were
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:45.17,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,just weak sounds or voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.10,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:49.81,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Until I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.14,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm slowly starting to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.28,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What I want
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.13,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,isn't those mysterious pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.37,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It must be something clearer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.02,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,more tangible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.54,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,All I can hear is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:12.45,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:30.03,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I keep seeing you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:33.45,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Have I found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:30.99,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like David.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:32.05,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,The future can't be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:33.92,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What is my relationship with Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:35.41,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:38.56,Episode-Title - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 7\N "Bicycle"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.41,0:23:38.27,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't look bad.
